{"tid":1551121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［年輕人對抗失格社會］好適合香港人睇嘅動畫短片The Box","createTime":"2019-09-08T00:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T02:25:36.000Z","uid":87507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54485d394c387931d1a8916e2f8eee9226e2069e","tid":1551121,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:13:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gNVqRC4mcSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgNVqRC4mcSI&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=a76d9299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gNVqRC4mcSI</a><br />\n<br />\n內容大概講述係一個了無生機嘅盒入面，人人都係只係訓教。<br />\n一個新生命(年輕人)嚟到嘅時候，新生命好有活力成日唱歌。啲老屎忽就嫌佢嘈叫佢咪搞咁多野，甚至call怪獸(政府)打壓年輕人，明明佢地都一樣咁驚怪獸，但都係唔敢好似年輕人咁反抗。<br />\n<br />\n最好笑係完左條片仲有一個彩蛋，係我地大部分人嘅生活寫照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b02363f3d8338cb40de18d0be8d38518a9b8fce","tid":1551121,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:26:47.000Z","msg":"睇完。但諗得好負面"},{"pid":"fe687432015a159a7d15402f951971974e7b35f2","tid":1551121,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b02363f3d8338cb40de18d0be8d38518a9b8fce","tid":1551121,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:26:47.000Z","msg":"睇完。但諗得好負面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"同身邊嘅情況一模一樣"},{"pid":"d13548ed24ff6f9915cacf66d3e1a3dccb9a41b5","tid":1551121,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe687432015a159a7d15402f951971974e7b35f2","tid":1551121,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b02363f3d8338cb40de18d0be8d38518a9b8fce","tid":1551121,"uid":87670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:26:47.000Z","msg":"睇完。但諗得好負面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"同身邊嘅情況一模一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"片尾條友走左出去 我淨係諗住呢條友係林鄭 反正大眾都無救 不如佢加入打壓既一方"}]}